Popular singer, Habeeb Okikiola aka Portable, has cried out that his life is under threat.
In videos posted on his Instagram, he said, “You say you are powerful but I have God, I know influential people and I have MOPOL.
ALSO READ: Portable’s car was completely destroyed, no one knows his whereabouts – Kemi Olunloyo alleges
“They want to kill me. They have given me seven days. He has asked them to kill me. He went to report me to the police, he doesn’t know policemen are my fans. He reported me to soldiers, soldiers guard me.”
He accused one Ija Omode Yusuf of being behind the threat on his life.
 
